Package builder.actions

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAction
    Interface for Builder Actions to allow undo/redo capability.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeBuilderLevelAction
    Changes the level in the level Builder adds the actions onto the undoStack, but doesn't allow for undo capability.
    ChangeDefaultFillAction
    Changes the default fillFrom reference for all the squares on the board.
    ChangeRefAction
    Changes the fillForm references from a point to another point; allows undo and redo capability.
    ChangeRefMapAction
    Changes the fillForm references for all the points; allows undo and redo.
    CopyStateAction<T extends ICopy>
    A generic save/load state action that can be used for undo/redo.
    SpecialMoveAction
    Allows change of whether a level can make certain special moves.
    StarThresholdAction
    Allows the change of star thresholds and stoes the index, value, and previous value.
